high_descs: Go to the bathtub on your left.
Pull the green sponge between the two rags out of the bathtub.
Turn around and go to the sink on your left.
Place the sponge in the sink, turn the water on, rinse out the sponge, turn the water off, then remove the sponge from the sink.
Turn around and go to the counter top across the room.
Place the sponge on the counter, in front of the pump bottle on the right.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean sponge on the counter.

high_descs: Pick up the sponge from the bathtub
Turn right and go to the sink
Put the sponge in the sink and turn on the water. Turn the water off and take the sponge out of the sink
Turn around and go to the cabinet against the wall
Place the sponge on top of the cabinet to the right of the tissue box
anns.task_desc: Put a cleaned sponge on top of a cabinet

high_descs: walk to the right side of the tub.
Pick up the sponge from in between the two pink rags.
Turn and walk to the sink.
Put the sponge in the sink, rinse it off with water, pick up the sponge from the sink.
Turn around and walk to the counter on the other side of the room.
Put the sponge down on the counter to the right of the tissue box.
anns.task_desc: To rinse off a sponge and put it on the counter.
